
** Echoing

Use the '@' to suppress the output of the command.

info:
	@egrep '^[a-z0-9-]+:' Makefile

** Multiple Targets

Multiple targets need also an *all* target to create all of the multiple
targets. Otherwise only the first target will be created.


<example>
files=abc.o bde.o
all: $(files)
$(files)
</example>
